{"tid":1751071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西環觀龍選區事件","createTime":"2019-11-24T15:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:21:05.000Z","uid":341080,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8a75b59f9a6da8331e872709e5f9e4f15d2f48","tid":1751071,"uid":341080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我在士美非路體育館現場，睇住件事發生。<br />\n<br />\n2個popo黎拎兩個箱走，一紅一綠，話係百年大樓有行動不便者，所以早五日已經申請咗另一區票箱可以拎觀龍區投票站投。換言之，一綠箱係堅摩選區的票。紅箱係機密文件。<br />\n<br />\n但係，成件事係冇人監住，主任冇講過在外面等點票的巿民聽呢兩個箱要去邊。有個巿民發現咗，負責票箱的職員落去截住個箱，但睇黎已經太遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8335a4fa0b9b058ff1fbfcc01c394299fb80f824","tid":1751071,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f9a894ee53cbf00cffa4bfd189fac4e2356adf2","tid":1751071,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f53b7f8c8f0c3243fc5e2bd034b7a4e70c3634c2","tid":1751071,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c7f9cefcba347259a4064e099a22e50972b53c","tid":1751071,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"447fef5e9fa3f18faa849f6a2ac77103c2fff0f8","tid":1751071,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d9514b75f20db22321e89f728f4739d337ad34c","tid":1751071,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"699ac003e85365b4558dfd3c69b9157d80f555b3","tid":1751071,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:44:36.000Z","msg":